text: Þis his þare X hida boc æt ubban tune þe eadwig cing gebocode æþerede his þeine on eche yrfe.
Þis synt þa land gemere to Ubbantune.
Aerest of langan forda on hægdune westewearde.
Þonon forþ andlang dic on bican brache andlang dic on finbeorh.
Of hundes geata swa cynrices gemære sceat & ubbantuninga gemære on wilig þonne up andlang wilig eft on langan ford.
